Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.18,0:00:16.51,Default,,0,0,0,,TONBO!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.55,0:01:36.59,Default,,0,0,0,,EPISODE 26: TONBO'S CHALLENGE\NTHE HEROINES OF KYUSHU
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.68,0:01:41.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}When she was little, Tonbo Oi moved to{\i0}\N{\i1}Hinoshima in the Tokara Islands.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.31,0:01:46.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}With her late father's beloved three-iron,{\i0}\N{\i1}she began her journey with golf.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.48,0:01:49.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Her natural talent for golf flourished,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.31,0:01:53.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tonbo went to high school in Kumamoto.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.82,0:01:59.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There, she achieved an incredible feat,{\i0}\N{\i1}winning the Kyushu Women's Championship.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.11,0:02:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Now, she's returned to Hinoshima,{\i0}\N{\i1}celebrated as a champion.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.45,0:02:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Igaiga. What's with the creepy face?\NYou're muttering away to yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.62,0:02:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! N-Nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.00,0:02:14.30,Default,,0,0,0,,How's the sunset on Hinoshima\Nfeel after all this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.38,0:02:17.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It's amazing, just like I remembered.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.67,0:02:19.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Hinoshima sure is a great place!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.97,0:02:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,But I bet your time off the island\Nwas pretty exciting.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.68,0:02:28.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course! It was\Na whirlwind of excitement!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.31,0:02:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What stood out the most to me…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.40,0:02:32.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.77,0:02:34.61,Default,,0,0,0,,The ramen we had in Kagoshima!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.69,0:02:35.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What?! Ramen?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.24,0:02:37.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Here you go!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.24,0:02:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this? I've never\Nhad anything like it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.50,0:02:51.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Seriously, you never lose your appetite,{\i0}\N{\i1}no matter where you are.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.08,0:02:55.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I was so nervous{\i0}\N{\i1}on the way to Mr. Udo's house.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.42,0:02:58.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Didn't you doze off hard{\i0}\N{\i1}on the bullet train?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.09,0:03:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I was blown away by how beautiful{\i0}\N{\i1}the driving range he runs is.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.60,0:03:06.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And at night, it's so bright!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.56,0:03:10.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Mr. Udo and his wife{\i0}\N{\i1}are also very cheerful.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.23,0:03:15.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yes, the customers love his wife, Yaya.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.77,0:03:17.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see what you've got.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.69,0:03:18.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A driver?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.11,0:03:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I was bewildered when he suddenly{\i0}\N{\i1}asked me to use a driver.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.20,0:03:28.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yeah, that really put me on edge.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.04,0:03:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.13,0:03:42.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Using a driver is really difficult…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.93,0:03:46.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh, and speaking of Mr. and Mrs. Udo…{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.56,0:03:47.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yeah?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.81,0:03:51.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}-The breakfast they served was so good!{\i0}\N{\i1}-What?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.39,0:03:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is breakfast the first thing that comes{\i0}\N{\i1}to mind when you think of them?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.06,0:03:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No-Not at all!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.44,0:03:59.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And their son, Hajime, is a golf coach.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.61,0:04:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Igarashi told me. Wanna come with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.24,0:04:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.53,0:04:08.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Over here, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.87,0:04:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Meet your new friend. From Tokara--
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.92,0:04:15.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Tonbo Oi! It's a pleasure to meet y--
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.63,0:04:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Try this one!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.05,0:04:24.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'd never been around so many{\i0}\N{\i1}people my age, so I was nervous.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.97,0:04:26.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And also,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.51,0:04:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hinoki and I are only a year apart,{\i0}\N{\i1}but she seems so grown-up.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.60,0:04:36.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's the first friend{\i0}\N{\i1}you made in Kumamoto, right?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.06,0:04:38.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never seen you before.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.82,0:04:42.11,Default,,0,0,0,,-Yes, right.\N-I'm Hinoki Otoha.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.19,0:04:44.66,Default,,0,0,0,,A sophomore in high school.\NNice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.66,0:04:55.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It's huge! And green! And beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.05,0:05:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, Tonbo! It's your course debut!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.26,0:05:11.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.44,0:05:18.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so low!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.65,0:05:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It was the first time you played{\i0}\N{\i1}on a real course. How was it?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.40,0:05:24.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's different from our island.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.19,0:05:28.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There are no strong sea winds,{\i0}\N{\i1}and the ball rolls differently.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.45,0:05:33.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Just like playing on Mr. Kuta's{\i0}\N{\i1}island course, it was so much fun!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.45,0:05:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Gaining new experiences{\i0}\N{\i1}and trying new things.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.04,0:05:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}-Just like Fukuta said.{\i0}\N{\i1}-Yeah.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.80,0:05:47.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright! This is too fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.47,0:05:48.34,Default,,0,0,0,,A driver?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.43,0:05:52.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's when you gave me a new club.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.10,0:05:54.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ah… That's right.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.14,0:05:57.81,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Is there a problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.90,0:06:00.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It's 15,309 yen!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.11,0:06:04.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I was so happy with your parting gift!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.19,0:06:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I felt so embarrassed…{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.20,0:06:08.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.57,0:06:11.99,Default,,0,0,0,,-Um. That's pretty cheap.\N-It's a used club, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.58,0:06:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't slice it there!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.17,0:06:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll go off the cliff!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.58,0:06:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}C'mon! I hope I chose the right driver!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.92,0:06:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The swallow maneuver!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.59,0:06:29.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.59,0:06:31.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.97,0:06:35.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It went through!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.02,0:06:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Go! Flying fish ball!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.19,0:06:42.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Everyone was blown away{\i0}\N{\i1}by your playing style.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.73,0:06:45.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I just played like I usually did, though.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.78,0:06:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's your "usual" playing style{\i0}\N{\i1}that blows me away as well.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.45,0:06:51.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.82,0:06:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't think we'd end up\Nat the same school.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.20,0:06:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm relieved!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.50,0:06:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I was nervous about\Ngoing to school on my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.00,0:07:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why are you crying?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.63,0:07:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's because you've grown{\i0}\N{\i1}into a high school student…{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.05,0:07:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Exchanging contact info with your senior…{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.68,0:07:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You said something similar{\i0}\N{\i1}at my graduation ceremony.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.81,0:07:17.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Igaiga, your nose is running!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.77,0:07:21.31,Default,,0,0,0,,A thirty-eight?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.06,0:07:24.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I said no more than one over!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.19,0:07:28.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's when you suddenly{\i0}\N{\i1}snapped at her father.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.94,0:07:31.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yeah, I just lost my temper{\i0}\N{\i1}for a second there.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.74,0:07:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,And what makes you think\Nit was just a little breeze?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.95,0:07:39.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You were indoors weren't you?\NHow could you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.54,0:07:44.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}In a scary face competition,{\i0}\N{\i1}you'd win for sure.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.71,0:07:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Come on…{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.30,0:07:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,-A competition?\N-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.43,0:07:56.01,Default,,0,0,0,,The Kyushu Women's Open is next month.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.10,0:07:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,They're holding it at Chuo Country Club!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.81,0:08:00.89,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you going to do, Tonbo?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.98,0:08:02.35,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.77,0:08:03.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.90,0:08:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I was shocked I would be{\i0}\N{\i1}participating in a tournament!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.44,0:08:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.48,0:08:11.70,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why Tonbo\Nleft her island in the first place!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.78,0:08:15.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hajime put in so much effort to help you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.74,0:08:18.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't thank the Udo family enough.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.41,0:08:22.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm putting Tonbo\Nin the Kyushu Women's Open!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.21,0:08:27.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And wasn't there someone else{\i0}\N{\i1}from the Udo family who helped you?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.21,0:08:29.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Someone else?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.76,0:08:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's there? Stay away from me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.93,0:08:38.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Calm down, Tonbo!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.93,0:08:40.89,Default,,0,0,0,,So sorry to scare you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.97,0:08:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,This used to be my bedroom, actually.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.52,0:08:47.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Nikome Udo, a tour pro.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.52,0:08:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She returns home feeling down in the dumps{\i0}\N{\i1}every time she fails to qualify.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.45,0:08:55.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I know that feeling all too well…{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.66,0:08:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She gave me golf shoes{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.16,0:09:03.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and she told me something very important{\i0}\N{\i1}for being able to continue playing golf.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.58,0:09:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want to be a pro someday, Tonbo?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.79,0:09:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,-I'm not sure.\N-I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.42,0:09:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You've never even been\Nin a competition before.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.09,0:09:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,That's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.89,0:09:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,,First, you have to fall in love with golf.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.18,0:09:21.39,Default,,0,0,0,,That comes first.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.43,0:09:23.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Fall in love with golf.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.43,0:09:28.61,Default,,0,0,0,,When you really love something,\Nyou can't help but do your best.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.06,0:09:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.78,0:09:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hinoki gave me a golfbag.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.99,0:09:35.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hajime gave me a six-iron.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.99,0:09:40.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And someone from the country club{\i0}\N{\i1}gave me a nine-iron.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.08,0:09:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Together with your three-iron,{\i0}\N{\i1}that's seven clubs in total.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.96,0:09:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}-That's called a half set.{\i0}\N{\i1}-I know that!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.55,0:09:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,A half set…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.97,0:09:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,That's so cool. I feel like a pro!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.56,0:10:07.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I crossed paths with someone on{\i0}\N{\i1}day one of the Kyushu Women's Open!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.90,0:10:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Tonbo!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.40,0:10:11.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It really is you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.11,0:10:12.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsubura!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.32,0:10:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You're really here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.32,0:10:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to high school in Kumamoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.78,0:10:21.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You're so brave. I'm so happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.87,0:10:31.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Igaiga. Grandpa Gon. Setsu. Yoko.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.71,0:10:34.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Bunpei. Hidaka.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.76,0:10:38.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My first tournament has started.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.01,0:10:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wish I'd been there!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.72,0:10:44.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Don't worry. I hit the ball{\i0}\N{\i1}all the way to the island.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.75,0:11:07.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.00,0:11:10.87,Default,,0,0,0,,N-Nice eagle.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.96,0:11:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}An eagle? That's one hell of a debut!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.09,0:11:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wish I could have seen it!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.55,0:11:19.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I shouldn't have gone back to the island!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.42,0:11:21.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hidaka and Bunpei would have been upset!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.22,0:11:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Mrs. Shima, from our group, was{\i0}\N{\i1}playing for the third time already.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.68,0:11:30.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She's such a nice person.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.81,0:11:34.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. Am I causing trouble?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.15,0:11:41.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ms. Matsuda, who was also in our group,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.57,0:11:44.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}was off her game, and I was scared of her.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.74,0:11:46.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But then, Mrs. Shima said…{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.20,0:11:48.37,Default,,0,0,0,,But you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.45,0:11:52.33,Default,,0,0,0,,you can't recover from\Nyour mistakes all at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.46,0:11:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a whole 18 holes\Nto set things straight.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.80,0:12:00.51,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're at the end of the game\Nand there's nothing left to do,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.05,0:12:03.64,Default,,0,0,0,,you still have your\Nwhole life ahead of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.05,0:12:06.39,Default,,0,0,0,,If you can improve\Nyour lifetime stroke average
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.47,0:12:09.39,Default,,0,0,0,,even by one point, that's\Nsomething to be proud of!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.10,0:12:13.81,Default,,0,0,0,,My lifetime average?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.90,0:12:16.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What wise words…{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.73,0:12:19.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Thanks to her words,{\i0}\N{\i1}someone who I thought was scary,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.74,0:12:22.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}suddenly became much more easygoing.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.78,0:12:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Wow! Number one! Incredible!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.20,0:12:30.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}-I wish I could have seen it…{\i0}\N{\i1}-Enough already!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.21,0:12:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Mrs. Shima…{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.08,0:12:37.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}-What a shame…{\i0}\N{\i1}-Yes.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.63,0:12:41.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But she told me something very important.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.55,0:12:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yes. It was good that you met her.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.72,0:12:46.43,Default,,0,0,0,,That's how much I love golf.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.89,0:12:51.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so glad I got to play\Nwith you, Mrs. Shima.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.64,0:12:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd love to play with you again someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.69,0:12:57.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Tonbo.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.61,0:13:05.49,Default,,0,0,0,,It sure is crowded.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.57,0:13:07.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}On the second day, I met someone new.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.45,0:13:11.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ema Kurisu, a former{\i0}\N{\i1}World Junior Champion.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.87,0:13:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A lefty?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.83,0:13:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She suffered a major left leg injury{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.84,0:13:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and started playing{\i0}\N{\i1}left-handed to overcome it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.43,0:13:35.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I played a round with her,{\i0}\N{\i1}Tsubura, and Hinoki.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.31,0:13:41.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Once again, I'll be your caddy, Hata.\NI look forward to playing with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.32,0:13:43.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.33,0:13:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ema's determination really inspired me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.54,0:14:03.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It reminded me of when Tsubura shared{\i0}\N{\i1}her dreams back on Hinoshima.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.26,0:14:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Her passion for golf…{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.43,0:14:08.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can learn from that myself.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.64,0:14:12.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Everyone's got this{\i0}\N{\i1}amazing dedication to the game.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.97,0:14:17.73,Default,,0,0,0,,In America, all sorts of scary creatures\Nlive in the lakes on golf courses.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.98,0:14:20.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean, alligators?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.44,0:14:26.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I lost my ability to swing and\Nmake shots as beautiful as yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.45,0:14:30.82,Default,,0,0,0,,However, it hasn't been all bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.91,0:14:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm happy to be able to play at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.37,0:14:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm grateful that I'm able to play golf.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.33,0:14:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I think that might be\Nmy greatest strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.63,0:14:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}On the second day, I scored 77,{\i0}\N{\i1}10 strokes worse than my opening round…{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.96,0:14:47.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's when…{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.85,0:14:55.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Tonbo!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.39,0:14:59.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing here?\NYou came to get me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.36,0:15:03.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You're doing great.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.82,0:15:08.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You started crying then.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.90,0:15:11.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Were you that happy to see me?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.70,0:15:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No! Nothing like that. I…{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.20,0:15:17.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I was just happy to see you{\i0}\N{\i1}after all that time.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.20,0:15:19.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I missed the island.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.46,0:15:23.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}-I was just hopesick!{\i0}\N{\i1}-You surely mean "homesick"?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.05,0:15:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Remember that tool you used\Nto dispatch octopi and fish?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.55,0:15:34.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}At first, I didn't understand your advice.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.56,0:15:37.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}-But it worked!{\i0}\N{\i1}-I know, right?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.44,0:15:45.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Were you surprised when you heard\NI was in first place on day one?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.82,0:15:48.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, it didn't surprise\Nme all that much.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.65,0:15:49.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.95,0:15:53.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I was happy more than anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.28,0:15:55.53,Default,,0,0,0,,And not only me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.08,0:15:58.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Everyone on the island was smiling.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.08,0:16:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Everyone on the island is rooting for you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.46,0:16:08.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like you've become\Nthe pride of the whole island.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.76,0:16:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,,They're happy you're one of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.64,0:16:16.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about your score!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.93,0:16:21.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Play your way! Show us\Nthat special Tonbo style!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.10,0:16:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.23,0:16:29.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Go! Flying fish ball!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.61,0:16:34.41,Default,,0,0,0,,What? That stance!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.29,0:16:40.29,Default,,0,0,0,,She avoided the sand!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.08,0:16:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.00,0:16:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew that would work! This is so fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.71,0:16:51.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Igaiga is over there. Alright.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.64,0:17:01.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright! Right on target! Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.48,0:17:09.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright! My first birdie!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.61,0:17:13.95,Default,,0,0,0,,If you make a mistake on this hole,\Nyou'll be down by four.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.03,0:17:16.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Down by four with three holes left.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.20,0:17:17.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You won't be able to win.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.33,0:17:22.29,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, don't hit a bogey\Nif you still want to win.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.54,0:17:27.67,Default,,0,0,0,,If I still want to win…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.17,0:17:32.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I was waiting for something{\i0}\N{\i1}to spark inside of you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.59,0:17:36.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yeah. I could feel it{\i0}\N{\i1}from the 15th hole onward.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.76,0:17:38.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What is this?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.55,0:17:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No. I want to win.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.76,0:17:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Everyone on the island{\i0}\N{\i1}will be so happy if I win.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.18,0:17:46.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I want to make them happy. I want to win.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.73,0:17:48.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I get it now.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.73,0:17:52.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm nervous.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.69,0:17:54.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm under pressure.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.70,0:17:57.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care about chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.62,0:18:02.45,Default,,0,0,0,,By acknowledging the pressure I'm under,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.12,0:18:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm ready to face it head on.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.08,0:18:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I may fail.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.04,0:18:12.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is a scary shot.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.05,0:18:16.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is the first time{\i0}\N{\i1}I've ever felt this.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.80,0:18:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So this is real golf.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.43,0:18:26.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Come on. Crab ball!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.77,0:18:29.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Please! Get there!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.19,0:18:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.37,0:18:42.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.58,0:18:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This was the hole where I first sensed{\i0}\N{\i1}the pressure you warned me about.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.33,0:18:51.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And I felt that up to the final hole.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.54,0:18:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tonbo…{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.92,0:18:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But you know, whenever{\i0}\N{\i1}I would overthink things,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.80,0:18:59.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I could hear you cheering me on.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.05,0:19:00.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Here I go.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.64,0:19:04.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like Igaiga told me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.52,0:19:09.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not aiming for the fairway at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.77,0:19:16.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just like I told her.\NThe score doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.28,0:19:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Give it your all! Win this thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.83,0:19:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Thanks to you, I finally realized{\i0}\N{\i1}the true meaning of golf.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.09,0:19:38.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So close!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.72,0:19:42.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why didn't it go in?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.51,0:19:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You jinxed it, Igaiga.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.97,0:19:47.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That was fun!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.02,0:19:57.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The last group was Tsubura,{\i0}\N{\i1}Hinoki, Ema, and me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.65,0:19:59.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Go through!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.57,0:20:03.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}By the third day,{\i0}\N{\i1}the strain on her leg had gotten worse.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.20,0:20:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.29,0:20:15.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But Ema was holding back{\i0}\N{\i1}the pain and fell down at the end.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.17,0:20:19.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That kind of mental resolve{\i0}\N{\i1}is rare among players.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.34,0:20:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Still, competitions can be ruthless…{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.60,0:20:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yahoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.14,0:20:34.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Now it's the playoffs, Hinoki!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.73,0:20:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,,No. You're wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.82,0:20:44.87,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.24,0:20:50.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Hinoki.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.29,0:20:55.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yesterday, on the fifth hole.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.54,0:20:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I made my ball move!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.96,0:20:59.67,Default,,0,0,0,,But I didn't report it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.46,0:21:04.05,Default,,0,0,0,,But I kept playing. I continued on!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.39,0:21:07.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.39,0:21:10.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.52,0:21:12.31,Default,,0,0,0,,…forfeit the game!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.14,0:21:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That must have been{\i0}\N{\i1}such a difficult situation for Hinoki.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.07,0:21:20.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A foul is a foul, though.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.19,0:21:22.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It took a lot of guts to confess that.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.49,0:21:23.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She has my respect.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.03,0:21:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Same.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.37,0:21:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You talked to Hinoki with kind words{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.99,0:21:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and Hajime encouraged her as well.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.16,0:21:38.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I was so happy for that.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.00,0:21:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Hinoki.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.59,0:21:43.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not going to quit, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.93,0:21:45.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Tonbo.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.43,0:21:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not quitting.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.31,0:21:58.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, Igaiga…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.36,0:22:03.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Since I left the island, I've\Ngrown to love golf even more.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.94,0:22:07.95,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not about setting goals\Nor aiming for something.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.07,0:22:11.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Just loving the game is enough for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.95,0:22:13.33,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I've realized.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.75,0:22:15.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.25,0:22:22.05,Default,,0,0,0,,And that means I'm going\Nto keep loving golf more and more!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.13,0:22:23.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.67,0:22:27.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's eat Grandpa Gon's fish and\NSetsu's cooking till we're stuffed!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.59,0:22:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Not training?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.72,0:22:31.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Typically Tonbo, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.93,0:22:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay! Time for a bath and then dinner!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.73,0:22:36.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright!
